race.comment: SERRAI (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.3 lengths away in second (19.78) behind Mepunga Rocky at Capalaba. Comes through a solid form race last start. Leading player again. KEEP PAYING (2) is in hot form after clocking a sharp 19.84 victory two back then followed up with a 30.21 win at this track over 520m last time. Has the ability and looks a key chance. NOPE ROPE (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to bounce back.
